title: Is There A Such Thing As Being Too Perfect? Keity Thinks So!
description:
Our producer Keity has a friend who recently started dating someone new. She is happy with this man and thinks he's wonderful. BUT Keity thinks there is something wrong with him. Is there a such thing as being too perfect? We discuss.
